Welcome to the \b internal \bt_name documentation!

This documentation covers everything you need to improve and fix the
\bt_name project.

@note
    If you're looking for the public libbabeltrace2 C&nbsp;API, see
    <code>doc/api/libbabeltrace2</code> and the
    <code>\--enable-api-doc</code> option of the \c configure script.

This project doesn't currently contain internal Python bindings
and testing documentation.

@section tree Source tree structure

All the source files of \bt_name are within the \c src directory. In
this documentation, all the paths, unless otherwise specified, are
relative to the \c src directory.

Within the \c src directory:

