@ingroup common-c

@code{.c}
#include "common/common.h"
@endcode

@defgroup common-c-enum-str Enumerator string utilities
@brief
    Enumerator string functions.

@ingroup common-c

@code{.c}
#include "common/common.h"
@endcode

@defgroup glib-c GLib helpers (C)
@brief
    GLib compatibility functions and utilities (C).

@code{.c}
#include "compat/glib.h"
#include "common/common.h"
@endcode

This topic offers both compatibility and helper C&nbsp;functions to work
with GLib.

\bt_name currently supports GLib&nbsp;&ge;&nbsp;2.28. This version is
missing a few useful functions which were introduced in subsequent
releases.
